      - No-extra-fields check: only the 9 in-scope content fields are
        populated (assigned_group, description, priority,
        requester_email, requester_name, status, subject, type) plus
        the 6 required sys_* housekeeping fields (sys_class_name,
        sys_created_by, sys_id, sys_package, sys_scope,
